t:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;\" />\n</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">发票内容可以选择商品明细、办公用品、电脑配件、耗材，建议您将发票内容开具为商品明细，否则您将无法享受产品厂商和高鸿商城的正常质保，高鸿商城不对此承担责任。</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">2</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">、每个包裹对应一张发票，不同库房发出的包裹开具不同的发票。</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;color:#484848;font-family:Tahoma, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:22px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;list-style-type:none;list-style-position:initial;list-style-image:initial;font-size:9pt;\">3</span><span style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-